sampleCellData.displayText: As stated before I've been a few SMPs before including - GrowthSMP, AzureSMP, PixieSMP and SovereignSMP. While I do have a set schedule for streams and my videos, I can be pretty flexible. I can be a bit on the reserved side at first but after you get to know me and especially if you get me on a topic I like, I may talk your ear off. I do like to try to change my skin for occasions whether the holidays or to fit my build or events as well.

While I do have a set schedule for streams and my videos, I can be pretty flexible. I can be a bit on the reserved side at first but after you get to know me and especially if you get me on a topic I like, I may talk your ear off. I do like to try to change my skin for occasions whether the holidays or to fit my build or events as well. "

sampleCellData.displayText: I'm very much primarily into automatic farms, in some cases designing my own. Recently, though I have been getting more into building, working on more larger scale stuff.
sampleCellData.rawValueJson: "I'm very much primarily into automatic farms, in some cases designing my own. Recently, though I have been getting more into building, working on more larger scale stuff."

sampleCellData.displayText: I'd like to revisit and expand on an old build of mine I called 'skylab'. It was essentially a big quartz disc over an ocean with some buildings. For 2.0 I'd probably add in more discs. perhaps built over a guardian farm. I have quite a geometric/futuristic build style so whatever I end up doing it's likely gonna feature lots of patterns and straight edges. As for shops, pretty much if I farm something I'll likely see if I can make a shop for it.

As for shops, pretty much if I farm something I'll likely see if I can make a shop for it.  "

sampleCellData.displayText: I's release just simple let's play videos every couple weeks or so. Similar to what I'm doing already with the Inter Realms SMP, alternating between servers for each video. I'm not much of a storyteller/lore person; I like to just show stuff as it is.
